# DeepFang Salvage Plan — v0.1 → v0.2

**Date:** 2026-05-04  
**Author:** Claude Sonnet 4.6 (analysis session with Sandra)  
**Status:** Approved for implementation

---

## Background: What v0.1 Got Right and Wrong

DeepFang v0.1.0 was generated by DeepSeek V4 Pro. The overall architecture — a three-stage sanitize → adjudicate → dispatch pipeline with Docker network isolation — is well-designed and genuinely useful. The problem is that two of the three pipeline containers were assigned to real open-source projects that don't expose the APIs they were expected to provide.

### The Fiction

| v0.1 Container | Image Used | What It Actually Is |
|----------------|-----------|---------------------|
| ZeroClaw sanitizer | `ghcr.io/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw:v0.7.4` | Personal AI assistant gateway (Rust). Tag `v0.7.4` doesn't exist; current is `v0.3.3-beta`. Doesn't expose `/sanitize`. |
| Moltbot worker | `ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw:latest` | "Moltbot" = "OpenClaw" = "ClawdBot" — all the same project, a Node.js personal assistant. Renamed multiple times due to trademark dispute with Anthropic. Doesn't expose `/execute`. |

The DeepSeek bridge (`containers/deepseek_bridge.py`) is real, complete, and correct. The supervisor, dashboard, and docker-compose network topology are all sound.

### What Stays

| Component | Verdict | Notes |
|-----------|---------|-------|
| `src/deepfang/main.py` | ✅ Keep | Pipeline logic, audit log, health checks clean |
| `src/deepfang/mcp_server.py` | ✅ Keep + minor fix | `deepfang_dispatch` bypass needs a guard; FastMCP 3.2 SSE mount needs update |
| `containers/deepseek_bridge.py` | ✅ Complete | Real working DeepSeek proxy, safe-fail defaults |
| `containers/Dockerfile.supervisor` | ✅ Keep | Both targets correct |
| `dashboard/` | ✅ Keep | React UI functional, needs `npm run build` |
| `docker-compose.yml` | ✅ Skeleton | Network topology correct; ports and images need replacing |
| `configs/zeroclaw/rules.yaml` | ✅ Salvage | Good rule intent; rename to `configs/sanitizer/rules.yaml` |
| `configs/moltbot/worker.yaml` | ✅ Salvage | Allowlist correct; rename to `configs/worker/worker.yaml` |
| `tests/test_supervisor.py` | ✅ Keep + expand | Basic structure fine |

