## Port Fix (Critical — Pre-Phase-1)

DeepFang v0.1 assigned ports 10930-10937, all of which conflict with existing fleet servers:

| v0.1 Port | Conflict |
|-----------|---------|
| 10930 | `songgeneration-mcp` SongGeneration-Studio |
| 10932 | `openclaude-mcp` MCP SSE backend |
| 10933 | `openclaude-mcp` React webapp |

**New port assignment:**

| Service | Old Port | New Port |
|---------|----------|----------|
| Supervisor MCP + API | 10930 | **10956** |
| Dashboard | 10931 | **10957** |
| Sanitizer Shim | 10932 | **10958** |
| DeepSeek Bridge | 10933 | **10959** |
| Worker | 10934 | **10960** |
| Prometheus | 10935 | **10961** |
| Loki | 10936 | **10962** |
| Grafana | 10937 | **10963** |

