```

The supervisor already mounts `dashboard/dist` as static files if it exists. No code changes needed.

### 1.7 start.ps1 Fleet Standard Compliance

Add `Require-Command` checks for `docker` and `node` per the fleet naked-PC install standard:

```powershell
function Require-Command($cmd) {
    if (-not (Get-Command $cmd -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue)) {
        Write-Error "$cmd not found. Install it and retry."
        exit 1
    }
}
Require-Command docker
Require-Command node
```

