## Phase 3 — Polish (estimated 0.5 days)

### 3.1 Content Hashing in Audit Log

Add `content_hash` field to every audit log entry in `main.py`. Required for the `deepfang_dispatch` guard in Phase 1.

### 3.2 Grafana Dashboard Provisioning

Add `configs/grafana/dashboards/deepfang.json` — a default dashboard showing:
- Pipeline request rate (sanitize/adjudicate/dispatch calls/min)
- Verdict distribution (approve vs deny %)
- Threat score histogram
- Service health over time

The supervisor already exposes Prometheus metrics via `prometheus-fastapi-instrumentator`. Just needs a provisioned dashboard.

### 3.3 WEBAPP_PORTS.md Update

Add the 8 new ports (10956-10963) to `D:\Dev\repos\mcp-central-docs\operations\WEBAPP_PORTS.md`.

